<title>UK: Eidos prices $50 million convertible bond.</title>
<headline>Eidos prices $50 million convertible bond.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-03-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following convertible bond has been priced by lead manager Deutsche Morgan Grenfell.</p>
<p> BORROWER   EIDOS PLC</p>
<p> AMT   *$50 MLN	 COUPON     6.25	MATURITY  **14.JUL.02</p>
<p> TYPE	 STRAIGHT  ISS PRICE  100.0     PAY DATE    14.APR.97</p>
<p> FULL FEES  2.50	LISTING    LONDON    PAY FREQ    SEMI-ANN</p>
<p> MOODY/S&amp;P  =	   DENOMS (K) 10	  SALE LIMITS =</p>
<p> NOTES     *PLUS GREENSHOE OF $7.5 MLN</p>
<p>	    **NOT CALLABLE FOR TWO YRS THREE MONTHS, THEREAFTER</p>
<p>		CALLABLE SUBJECT TO 140 PCT HURDLE</p>
<p>		PREMIUM IS 23.77 PCT</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
